Ant-Based-Routing
=================

Exam project for Physics of Algorithms

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -s, --single          run a single ant-testcase
  -p, --pheromone-test  plot the formulas used for pheromone trailing &
                        evaporation

  Options for running tests of multiple cases:
    -m, --multi         run a series of multiple ant-testcases
    -c CASE_NO, --cases=CASE_NO
                        define the number of testcases, default = 100

  Options for dynamically changing test cases:
    -d, --dynamic-test  run a dynamically changing ant-testcase
    -i DYNAMIC_ITE, --iterations=DYNAMIC_ITE
                        define the number of iterations, default = 100
    -r, --randomized    the changes to the test graph are made by random,
                        instead of using predefined changes

